Popular Nigerian skit maker, Debo Adebayo, known on stage as Mr. Macaroni or Freaky Daddy, clocked 29, Tuesday, May 3. Celebrating himself, Macaroni shared stunning photos of himself rocking Yoruba attire which had gotten fans thrilled on social media. Posting on his Facebook page, he said, “It’s my birthday and I’m so thankful”. Many fans had also taken to his social media accounts to wish him a happy birthday. The actor and activist is best known for his Instagram comedy videos, where he plays the role of a “sugar daddy”. He is famously known for the phrases of “Ooin” and “You are doing well”. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com